WEBVTT

00:16.160 --> 00:18.360
[Huiyin Hall]

00:20.000 --> 00:21.930
Your Highness, please take a rest.

00:22.160 --> 00:23.760
You've been writing all day.

00:24.480 --> 00:26.280
Hasn't Xiao Wuyi confessed yet?

00:26.710 --> 00:28.030
Forgive me, Your Highness.

00:28.030 --> 00:29.350
No matter how he's tortured,

00:29.350 --> 00:31.550
Xiao Wuyi remains silent.

00:31.830 --> 00:33.320
He only asked the jailers
for a brush and ink

00:33.320 --> 00:34.920
to finish his military book.

00:35.110 --> 00:36.520
Without Your Highness's permission,

00:36.520 --> 00:37.670
the jailers didn't dare to give him those.

00:37.670 --> 00:41.000
So Xiao Wuyi dips his finger in blood
and continues to write.

00:43.200 --> 00:44.240
What about the divorce paper?

00:44.240 --> 00:45.300
He didn't write it.

00:45.320 --> 00:46.650
Then force him to write!

00:48.710 --> 00:51.100
Once it's written,
send it to Prince Jing'an's Mansion!

00:51.100 --> 00:52.820
Tell the Commandant of Justice that

00:52.820 --> 00:55.710
the evidence of Prince Jing'an's Household's
treason and corruption is conclusive.

00:55.710 --> 00:57.910
If he can't get Xiao Wuyi's confession,

00:57.930 --> 00:59.110
Xiao Ju's will do,

00:59.110 --> 01:00.200
or Xiao Yao's!

01:02.920 --> 01:04.180
Grand Tutor was right.

01:05.150 --> 01:07.680
Prince Jing'an's Household
is too stubborn.

01:08.680 --> 01:11.760
We might as well take this opportunity
and completely bring them down.

01:11.760 --> 01:12.400
Yes.

02:40.020 --> 02:43.910
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

02:44.070 --> 02:46.880
[Episode 23]

03:06.530 --> 03:09.060
Xiao and his 2 sons embezzled canal funds,

03:09.470 --> 03:10.490
illegally sold military supplies,

03:10.490 --> 03:11.820
and committed treason.

03:12.150 --> 03:13.680
Their mansion is now sealed off.

03:13.680 --> 03:14.800
By the Regent's grace,

03:14.800 --> 03:16.750
those who are not members
of the Xiao family may leave.

03:16.750 --> 03:19.400
Anyone who refuses will be sealed
inside the mansion immediately.

03:19.400 --> 03:20.490
Except for the Dowager Princess,

03:20.490 --> 03:21.440
everyone else has left.

03:21.440 --> 03:23.520
Master He is just a teacher
hired by our family.

03:23.520 --> 03:25.630
And Ruisheng is our physician.

03:25.950 --> 03:27.920
Aren't they a goddaughter and a concubine?

03:27.920 --> 03:28.680
And what about the child?

03:28.680 --> 03:29.970
Master He belongs to the He family

03:29.970 --> 03:31.360
and has nothing to do with the Xiaos.

03:31.360 --> 03:32.430
As for Yu Ruisheng,

03:32.430 --> 03:34.420
she has never been
part of Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

03:34.420 --> 03:36.079
She is an official
of the Beifu Army Medical Office

03:36.079 --> 03:37.329
and receives her salary from Beifu.

03:37.329 --> 03:38.260
As for Duan Ziqi,

03:38.380 --> 03:39.990
he is certainly not Xiao Wuyi's son.

03:39.990 --> 03:41.120
And the Dowager Princess—

03:41.120 --> 03:42.480
if I remember correctly,

03:42.480 --> 03:45.170
according to the laws of Ye,
women over fifty awaiting trial

03:45.170 --> 03:46.500
can be confined at home.

03:46.840 --> 03:47.640
Is that right?

03:48.390 --> 03:49.110
As for me...

03:51.430 --> 03:52.829
What is that in your hand?

03:52.870 --> 03:55.030
This is Young Lord Xiao's divorce paper.

03:55.030 --> 03:56.710
Your Highness, the Regent wants you

03:56.710 --> 03:58.570
to think carefully for yourself.

04:03.280 --> 04:04.630
Please convey my word

04:04.850 --> 04:06.040
to Prince Qi.

04:06.730 --> 04:09.170
Tomorrow is the deadline.

04:11.780 --> 04:12.570
Report!

04:15.500 --> 04:16.570
Your Highness,

04:16.750 --> 04:18.240
Liu Zhaolin,
an editor from Zhengtong Bookstore,

04:18.240 --> 04:19.769
has come to turn himself in.

04:19.829 --> 04:21.560
Wasn't Liu Zhaolin already...

04:22.190 --> 04:22.750
Report!

04:24.400 --> 04:26.400
Congratulations, Your Highness.

04:26.900 --> 04:27.830
For what?

04:28.190 --> 04:29.190
Your Highness,

04:29.240 --> 04:31.920
the blood stasis in Xiao Wuyi's brain
has been there for nearly 3 years

04:31.920 --> 04:33.720
and has become a chronic illness.

04:33.720 --> 04:34.930
Rest assured, Your Highness.

04:34.930 --> 04:36.780
Once his meridians are completely blocked,

04:36.780 --> 04:37.950
he won't survive.

04:38.310 --> 04:39.400
In my humble opinion,

04:39.400 --> 04:41.530
Xiao Wuyi will not live past this year.

04:42.960 --> 04:43.690
How dare you!

04:45.430 --> 04:47.760
When did I ever say
I wanted Xiao Wuyi dead?

04:48.480 --> 04:49.409
I'm telling you.

04:49.690 --> 04:51.350
If Xiao Wuyi doesn't recover,

04:51.480 --> 04:54.000
I will bury the entire
Imperial Medical Bureau with him!

04:54.000 --> 04:54.600
Get out!

04:56.010 --> 04:56.530
Yes.

05:01.700 --> 05:02.830
If we don't eliminate Northern Qin

05:02.830 --> 05:03.680
and reclaim our land,

05:03.680 --> 05:05.390
there won't be true peace!

05:05.920 --> 05:06.600
Yizhi.

05:07.390 --> 05:08.920
This is what you told me yourself

05:08.920 --> 05:10.450
while fleeing to Jiankang.

05:11.000 --> 05:12.950
Have you forgotten?

05:16.230 --> 05:17.760
Don't be trapped in the past

05:18.200 --> 05:20.130
and let it become your inner demon.

05:21.960 --> 05:23.690
You are not this kind of person.

05:25.040 --> 05:25.800
Report!

05:26.890 --> 05:27.750
Your Highness,

05:28.720 --> 05:29.480
the jailers said that

05:29.480 --> 05:31.040
before Young Lord Xiao fainted, he said

05:31.040 --> 05:32.230
he had no crimes to confess,

05:32.230 --> 05:33.760
and that if he must confess,

05:34.220 --> 05:37.280
this military book written in blood
is his confession.

05:40.870 --> 05:41.870
Summon Xie Jiayu.

05:43.159 --> 05:43.760
Yes.

05:45.070 --> 05:45.680
No.

05:47.270 --> 05:47.950
Forget it.

05:49.390 --> 05:51.480
Have Xie Jiayu go directly to the prison

05:51.480 --> 05:52.740
and take Xiao Wuyi out.

05:54.000 --> 05:54.490
Yes.

05:57.180 --> 06:00.500
[Court of Judicial Review]

06:38.510 --> 06:39.310
You dictate,

06:38.600 --> 06:43.770
♪ What's the cost
of going against the wind? ♪

06:41.620 --> 06:42.880
and I'll write it down.

06:44.590 --> 06:48.280
♪ Knowing you, knowing me,
we live up to our promises ♪

06:48.300 --> 06:52.500
♪ Aligning the traces of our conviction ♪

06:52.620 --> 06:55.090
♪ As long as I'm with you ♪

06:53.720 --> 06:55.110
Anyone who uses formations...

06:55.110 --> 06:58.090
♪ The journey can stretch on forever ♪

06:58.110 --> 07:01.870
♪ Even if it puts my life on the line ♪

07:01.890 --> 07:04.580
♪ I shall never forget ♪

07:04.670 --> 07:09.050
♪ Let me dash toward where you are ♪

07:09.080 --> 07:12.510
♪ To seek out my own sanctuary ♪

07:12.530 --> 07:15.320
♪ Life hurries by, yet you alone ♪

07:15.340 --> 07:18.340
♪ Illuminate me
with your blazing radiance ♪

07:18.370 --> 07:22.420
♪ Let me burn with courage
as I forge ahead ♪

07:22.450 --> 07:25.930
♪ Your hand in my hand ♪

07:25.950 --> 07:28.870
♪ Our love knows no bounds
of time or space ♪

07:28.900 --> 07:34.430
♪ Two hearts together
until the end of time ♪

07:36.640 --> 07:37.350
Done.

07:40.320 --> 07:42.050
Can you go home with me now?

07:44.360 --> 07:45.880
Pack these manuscripts up

07:47.360 --> 07:49.960
and give them to Prince Qi
and the Department of State Affairs.

07:49.960 --> 07:51.480
This is your life's work.

07:52.120 --> 07:53.290
If you teach them,

07:54.000 --> 07:56.090
aren't you afraid of being replaced?

07:56.950 --> 07:58.680
Isn't that exactly what I want?

07:59.630 --> 08:00.830
Don't you want

08:00.830 --> 08:02.630
there to be more Xiao Wuyis in Ye?

08:03.070 --> 08:05.400
Are you really making your final arrange—

08:11.560 --> 08:12.850
Even if you want to die,

08:14.480 --> 08:16.610
you have to hold on for a few more years.

08:18.040 --> 08:18.750
Right now,

08:20.280 --> 08:22.600
the world needs an invincible Xiao Wuyi.

08:24.410 --> 08:26.170
Let's go. Let's go home.

08:27.270 --> 08:28.070
Let's go home.

08:40.450 --> 08:41.020
Let's go.

08:56.290 --> 08:56.930
Wuyi!

08:59.510 --> 09:00.080
Mother?

09:02.130 --> 09:02.840
Father?

09:03.920 --> 09:04.450
Brother?

09:07.740 --> 09:08.390
You...

09:10.360 --> 09:11.240
Let's go home.

09:15.550 --> 09:16.730
That's my son!

09:16.900 --> 09:17.850
Be gentle!

09:18.370 --> 09:20.900
How can he stand you
patting him like that now?

09:24.880 --> 09:25.430
Let's go.

09:26.390 --> 09:27.030
Okay.

09:28.150 --> 09:29.000
Let's go home.

09:29.220 --> 09:32.730
[Shezhang Hall]

09:34.840 --> 09:36.370
Why did you let Xiao Wuyi go?

09:36.810 --> 09:37.450
You...

09:40.400 --> 09:41.060
This was...

09:42.320 --> 09:44.240
This was the only chance to bring
Prince Jing'an's Household down

09:44.240 --> 09:46.510
and take back the command
of Beifu Army!

09:47.320 --> 09:49.320
Don't you want to avenge

09:49.320 --> 09:50.050
your mother?

09:50.720 --> 09:52.850
If Xiao Ju hadn't concealed the truth,

09:53.440 --> 09:56.550
how could the An and Lu families
have been wrongfully destroyed?

09:56.550 --> 09:57.480
Xie Jiayu brought

09:57.480 --> 10:01.080
the letters between you and the wet nurse
of Prince Qi's Mansion,

10:01.120 --> 10:03.040
threatening to reveal my identity

10:03.040 --> 10:04.500
to make me let Xiao Wuyi go.

10:04.720 --> 10:07.010
Should I have let him go or not?

10:11.120 --> 10:13.250
So she came to me specifically that day

10:14.010 --> 10:15.370
for this?

10:16.460 --> 10:19.360
Oh, right, Liu Zhaolin turned himself in.

10:24.840 --> 10:25.390
Him?

10:27.170 --> 10:28.630
He wouldn't dare say much.

10:29.200 --> 10:32.330
Yes, he has committed suicide
out of fear of punishment.

10:34.050 --> 10:35.060
The Commandant of Justice also went to
Lane 3

10:35.060 --> 10:36.790
of Shanghe Ward to search and seal it,

10:36.790 --> 10:38.630
trying to catch those scholars
who had helped Liu Zhaolin

10:38.630 --> 10:40.490
forge the embezzlement ledgers.

10:40.670 --> 10:42.800
Unfortunately, he was a step too late.

10:45.540 --> 10:46.230
Also...

10:50.720 --> 10:51.480
Father,

10:52.490 --> 10:54.100
I only have one mother,

10:54.840 --> 10:56.640
and that is Prince Qi's Consort.

10:56.910 --> 10:58.320
Back then,
Prince Qi's Consort gave her life

10:58.320 --> 10:59.890
in exchange for my sister's life and mine.

10:59.890 --> 11:01.490
I have never had a 2nd mother.

11:02.180 --> 11:02.910
Avenging her

11:03.870 --> 11:05.120
is your obsession,

11:05.910 --> 11:07.030
not mine.

11:21.430 --> 11:22.190
Hurry!

11:23.120 --> 11:24.390
Did Liu Zhaolin mention

11:24.390 --> 11:26.600
who gave him the orders before he died?

11:26.800 --> 11:27.520
No.

11:27.580 --> 11:28.340
He didn't?

11:28.480 --> 11:30.740
Liu Zhaolin's original surname was Pei.

11:30.840 --> 11:32.960
He and He Yuanji, the former Heir's Consort
of Prince Jing'an's Mansion,

11:32.960 --> 11:34.270
were childhood sweethearts.

11:34.270 --> 11:37.000
After He married into
Prince Jing'an's Mansion,

11:37.170 --> 11:38.930
he couldn't accept losing her,

11:39.120 --> 11:40.510
so out of resentment,

11:40.630 --> 11:41.920
he deliberately framed them.

11:41.920 --> 11:45.000
He even bribed the scholars
in Lane 3 of Shanghe Ward

11:45.510 --> 11:48.080
to forge the evidence
of corruption with him.

11:48.870 --> 11:50.240
When the matter was exposed,

11:50.240 --> 11:52.120
he committed suicide
to atone for his crimes

11:52.120 --> 11:53.980
and clear the Xiao family's name.

11:54.080 --> 11:55.270
He was quite noble.

11:56.490 --> 12:00.880
[Court of Judicial Review]

12:06.870 --> 12:07.910
It's you?

12:09.030 --> 12:10.790
The moment I was imprisoned,

12:11.200 --> 12:12.510
I was reminded of

12:13.140 --> 12:14.720
an old story that circulated

12:14.720 --> 12:16.840
in the inner palace of the Capital.

12:17.390 --> 12:20.120
When you used the collapse
of the grain canal

12:20.640 --> 12:23.840
to try to wipe out
the entire Prince Jing'an's Household,

12:24.550 --> 12:26.550
it further confirmed my guess.

12:27.270 --> 12:30.320
The rumors about you
and Noble Concubine An back then

12:33.630 --> 12:34.390
were true.

12:40.120 --> 12:42.150
Back then, you knew it was an unjust case,

12:42.150 --> 12:44.080
yet you still sent the two noble families—

12:44.080 --> 12:46.540
hundreds of lives—to the execution ground.

12:46.590 --> 12:47.600
What I am doing now

12:47.600 --> 12:49.480
is merely returning an eye for an eye.

12:49.480 --> 12:51.360
Back then, the noble families
held absolute power.

12:51.360 --> 12:52.440
They defied the imperial authority

12:52.440 --> 12:53.600
and oppressed the people,

12:53.600 --> 12:54.960
making life impossible for them

12:54.960 --> 12:57.120
and leading rebel armies
to rise up everywhere.

12:57.120 --> 12:58.670
So you could disregard right and wrong

12:58.670 --> 13:00.130
and kill innocent people?

13:00.150 --> 13:02.810
The An and Lu families
never committed treason!

13:04.120 --> 13:05.650
Princess Pingning has been

13:06.360 --> 13:09.920
secretly operating in the Capital
and has obtained solid evidence.

13:09.920 --> 13:11.450
In the An-Lu case back then,

13:12.240 --> 13:13.670
you knew the truth

13:13.670 --> 13:14.870
but did not report it.

13:15.440 --> 13:16.840
Oh, you, Xiao Ju.

13:17.960 --> 13:21.960
You earned your title as Prince Jing'an

13:23.680 --> 13:25.800
on the blood of our noble families.

13:28.240 --> 13:29.080
I admit

13:30.240 --> 13:31.320
I am not innocent.

13:34.050 --> 13:35.510
But for the poor scholars,

13:36.360 --> 13:37.870
for Emperor and Empress Wenxi,

13:37.870 --> 13:39.200
and even more, for Ye,

13:39.480 --> 13:41.550
I had to burn my boats.

13:42.750 --> 13:44.080
As for you, Grand Tutor,

13:44.670 --> 13:46.910
as the head of the noble families,

13:48.030 --> 13:49.560
our stances are different.

13:50.510 --> 13:52.360
But speaking of wrongful deaths,

13:52.360 --> 13:53.440
to whom should those poor scholars

13:53.440 --> 13:56.240
wrongfully killed
by the An and Lu families

13:57.410 --> 13:59.890
cry out for justice?

14:04.300 --> 14:08.660
If the An and Lu families
deserved to be punished

14:09.030 --> 14:11.670
for overseeing
the waterway construction back then,

14:11.670 --> 14:14.720
then dare you say Xiao Yao
was entirely blameless

14:14.840 --> 14:19.150
for the collapse of the grain canal?

14:20.360 --> 14:24.030
Is he really innocent?

14:32.910 --> 14:36.390
Corruption and smuggling
may have been false accusations,

14:37.250 --> 14:38.910
but the grain canal collapse—

14:40.360 --> 14:41.290
I don't think so.

16:04.650 --> 16:05.910
Xiao Wuyi, you lied to me.

16:05.910 --> 16:07.000
You can see.

16:08.510 --> 16:10.360
This is called locating things by sound.

16:10.360 --> 16:12.670
I have been practicing it
for the past 2 years.

16:12.670 --> 16:14.080
Sooner or later, I will lose my sight.

16:14.080 --> 16:16.010
I can't be completely unprepared.

16:17.420 --> 16:18.820
Let go of me. Let me get up.

16:21.200 --> 16:22.200
Let go!

16:26.270 --> 16:26.910
Xiao Wuyi.

16:27.270 --> 16:29.070
Why didn't you tell me 2 years ago

16:29.480 --> 16:32.140
that the blood stasis
would keep getting worse?

16:32.570 --> 16:35.140
You are cruel,
planning to leave me behind.

16:35.570 --> 16:37.120
Aren't you afraid I'll back out?

16:37.120 --> 16:38.650
What can you do? Divorce me?

16:38.680 --> 16:41.610
After all, you've already burned
the divorce paper.

16:46.000 --> 16:46.630
You...

16:55.910 --> 16:56.970
Why are you crying?

17:02.870 --> 17:04.680
This blood stasis cannot be cured.

17:04.680 --> 17:05.880
Even if I had told you,

17:06.270 --> 17:08.270
it would have only added to your worries.

17:08.270 --> 17:09.930
But if you had told me earlier,

17:10.270 --> 17:12.670
I wouldn't have left you
in the past 2 years.

17:13.160 --> 17:15.290
And I wouldn't have been so oblivious,

17:16.069 --> 17:18.130
thinking we still had plenty of time.

17:23.480 --> 17:24.349
Alright.

17:26.790 --> 17:30.250
These past 2 years you've been
following the map to find mines,

17:30.880 --> 17:32.470
traveling thousands of miles

17:32.470 --> 17:34.870
and seeing the world
and all living beings.

17:35.240 --> 17:37.200
You opened branches
of Miraculous Craft across Ye

17:37.200 --> 17:38.310
to help the people.

17:39.590 --> 17:40.920
Are you happy?

17:48.790 --> 17:51.250
Your happiness
is the most important thing.

17:56.830 --> 17:58.720
Xiao Wuyi, I'm telling you.

17:59.440 --> 18:00.640
I haven't finished burning

18:00.640 --> 18:01.700
the divorce paper.

18:01.920 --> 18:02.880
There's still half left.

18:02.880 --> 18:03.750
If you ever

18:03.750 --> 18:05.030
hide anything

18:05.030 --> 18:05.830
from me again,

18:06.400 --> 18:07.920
anyone who wants to be the Heir's Consort
can have the title.

18:07.920 --> 18:09.320
I'm not doing it anymore.

18:13.000 --> 18:15.350
Trying to trick me? You want to back out?

18:17.110 --> 18:17.970
My blueprints!

18:19.480 --> 18:21.110
Xiao Wuyi, you can see.

18:24.310 --> 18:25.000
I can't see.

18:34.830 --> 18:36.790
Ziqi, listen to me.

18:37.110 --> 18:37.880
If you ever meet

18:37.880 --> 18:39.440
someone like your father,

18:39.440 --> 18:40.510
stay away from him,

18:40.690 --> 18:42.290
or he'll ruin your good name.

18:42.510 --> 18:44.640
What kind of person is he?

18:45.810 --> 18:47.240
To coax a lady,

18:47.550 --> 18:49.480
he calls a terminal illness a cold.

18:49.600 --> 18:50.880
He doesn't take care of himself

18:50.880 --> 18:52.750
and refuses
to take his condition seriously.

18:52.750 --> 18:53.830
But Mother,

18:54.270 --> 18:56.730
I don't want to study medicine
in the future.

18:56.830 --> 18:57.880
Then what do you want to study?

18:57.880 --> 18:59.200
I want to study poison.

19:00.110 --> 19:01.000
Say that again.

19:01.200 --> 19:04.260
I also want to learn Auntie Jiayu's
mechanical skills.

19:04.310 --> 19:06.110
If I can combine the two of them,

19:06.270 --> 19:07.670
it will be very powerful.

19:07.830 --> 19:09.880
That day, I even saw...

19:10.830 --> 19:12.720
Mother, have mercy!

19:14.300 --> 19:15.780
Duan Ziqi, come back here!

19:16.110 --> 19:17.920
Hang out less with your Auntie Jiayu!

19:17.920 --> 19:19.750
If you dare to touch her alchemy furnace,

19:19.750 --> 19:21.150
I'll chop off your hands!

19:21.440 --> 19:22.110
See?

19:22.750 --> 19:24.210
What have you taught Ziqi?

19:25.440 --> 19:27.570
It's clearly you who refuses to let go.

19:31.350 --> 19:32.240
What is this?

19:32.640 --> 19:34.170
This is a cane I made for you.

19:35.110 --> 19:36.570
It has a mechanism inside.

19:37.550 --> 19:40.410
It can be retracted into your sleeve
when not in use.

19:40.590 --> 19:42.240
But you've learned
to locate things by sound.

19:42.240 --> 19:43.640
I don't think you need it.

19:44.110 --> 19:45.040
Who says I don't?

19:48.400 --> 19:49.270
Xie Jiayu.

19:51.830 --> 19:54.890
Actually, the divorce paper
I wrote in prison was fake.

19:57.030 --> 19:58.690
I never wanted to divorce you.

20:02.200 --> 20:03.070
I know.

20:04.270 --> 20:05.270
Two years ago,

20:05.790 --> 20:06.920
Ruisheng told me

20:08.160 --> 20:10.400
there was a way to clear my blood stasis,

20:10.680 --> 20:11.880
but it was very risky.

20:13.070 --> 20:14.110
If it failed,

20:15.680 --> 20:17.480
I could lose my life at any time.

20:20.590 --> 20:22.050
But for the sake of reform,

20:22.920 --> 20:24.650
I chose not to take that chance.

20:27.200 --> 20:27.880
I'm sorry.

20:28.510 --> 20:29.880
Call me selfish

20:30.480 --> 20:31.280
or shameless.

20:33.030 --> 20:35.430
Even knowing
that I am destined to fail you,

20:38.030 --> 20:39.350
I will never let you go.

20:43.860 --> 20:46.440
If Ruisheng knows
you're not resting properly

20:46.440 --> 20:48.240
and that you're shedding tears,

20:48.400 --> 20:49.660
she'll scold me again.

20:51.110 --> 20:52.170
She wouldn't dare.

20:53.590 --> 20:55.050
You are my Heir's Consort.

21:01.750 --> 21:03.750
I lost my parents when I was young.

21:04.880 --> 21:05.550
Mother,

21:06.340 --> 21:07.070
Grand Tutor,

21:07.320 --> 21:08.590
Lejun, and Mao

21:09.880 --> 21:11.590
have also left me one by one.

21:13.550 --> 21:14.440
My whole life,

21:15.550 --> 21:18.150
it seems I've been learning
how to say goodbye.

21:21.030 --> 21:22.200
So don't worry.

21:24.500 --> 21:26.300
I am very good at saying goodbye.

21:29.480 --> 21:31.080
Even if that day really comes

21:31.440 --> 21:32.400
and you leave me,

21:36.030 --> 21:38.030
I will cry for you for a month at most.

21:40.790 --> 21:42.480
No, 3 months.

21:49.250 --> 21:51.180
As long as you promise me one thing,

21:53.490 --> 21:55.490
you won't be breaking your promise.

21:57.270 --> 21:57.880
Alright?

22:01.400 --> 22:02.200
Tell me.

22:05.750 --> 22:06.880
Whether it is 3 years

22:07.680 --> 22:08.680
or 5 years,

22:10.270 --> 22:11.400
from today on,

22:12.350 --> 22:14.550
forget the deadline Ruisheng gave you.

22:15.680 --> 22:16.550
No matter when,

22:19.000 --> 22:21.660
as long as you remember
that I am waiting for you,

22:22.310 --> 22:23.510
can you hold on for me

22:24.640 --> 22:26.160
for as long as you can?

22:27.110 --> 22:28.270
Let's go as far

22:28.270 --> 22:29.330
as we can together.

22:31.940 --> 22:33.600
I only need you to do your best,

22:34.330 --> 22:35.660
and I will do my best too.

22:38.720 --> 22:40.980
Then I won't see it
as you letting me down.

22:41.920 --> 22:43.580
But 3 months is just too short.

22:44.750 --> 22:46.010
It really is too short.

22:47.270 --> 22:48.440
How about 3 years?

22:49.110 --> 22:50.310
Forget me

22:52.590 --> 22:53.990
3 years after I die, okay?

22:54.550 --> 22:56.550
Can't you just say you will try harder

22:56.550 --> 22:57.790
to stay alive?

23:04.400 --> 23:05.070
Okay.

23:18.270 --> 23:21.180
Rest assured. Although His Highness
doesn't care about his life,

23:21.180 --> 23:22.250
as a physician,

23:22.280 --> 23:24.140
I still care about my reputation.

23:24.240 --> 23:26.640
I will do everything I can
to keep him alive.

23:32.110 --> 23:33.310
Thank you, Ruisheng.

23:35.200 --> 23:36.830
Fortunately, with you here now,

23:36.830 --> 23:39.230
my chances of success are actually higher.

23:40.550 --> 23:42.750
But he has put off treatment for so long.

23:44.600 --> 23:46.080
Life is truly magical.

23:46.830 --> 23:49.680
Sometimes, the will to live
matters more than anything else.

23:49.680 --> 23:52.210
In my eyes, Xiao Wuyi,
the commander of Beifu,

23:52.290 --> 23:53.940
was once more like

23:54.400 --> 23:55.730
a cold lifeless weapon.

23:56.480 --> 23:58.760
He gave almost everything for this world.

23:58.760 --> 24:01.350
He clearly took the world
as his responsibility,

24:01.350 --> 24:02.480
but it seemed

24:02.790 --> 24:05.720
he had never been attached
to anything in this world.

24:07.070 --> 24:08.020
Until he met you.

24:13.240 --> 24:14.750
People with aspirations cling to life,

24:14.750 --> 24:16.080
and martyrs seek death.

24:18.230 --> 24:18.990
Jiayu.

24:20.160 --> 24:21.420
You must hold onto him.

24:41.610 --> 24:43.410
You know your days are numbered.

24:43.440 --> 24:45.350
Five or ten years

24:45.830 --> 24:48.290
won't be enough
to complete your grand plan.

24:48.800 --> 24:52.200
That's why you're in such a rush
to complete the Beifu Reform.

24:54.030 --> 24:55.160
These past few days,

24:55.340 --> 24:56.720
I've been reading the military strategies
and essays

24:56.720 --> 24:57.850
you wrote in prison.

24:58.470 --> 24:59.920
You knew my background

24:59.940 --> 25:01.050
but said nothing,

25:01.270 --> 25:02.070
because you were certain

25:02.070 --> 25:03.830
that I would eventually agree with you.

25:03.830 --> 25:05.510
You were also certain I would march north,

25:05.510 --> 25:06.240
weren't you?

25:08.440 --> 25:09.880
Over 20 years have passed.

25:09.880 --> 25:10.830
How many survivors of Ye

25:10.830 --> 25:12.350
are being treated like cattle and slaves
by Northern Qin

25:12.350 --> 25:14.410
on the lands that once belonged to Ye?

25:14.640 --> 25:15.310
To this day,

25:15.310 --> 25:17.910
they are still waiting for
Crown Prince Wenxi.

25:18.110 --> 25:20.550
But what about 30 or 40 years from now?

25:22.270 --> 25:24.870
Yizhi, you are different
from the Grand Tutor.

25:25.390 --> 25:26.480
The noble families don't care about
reclaiming our land

25:26.480 --> 25:28.200
and are content to indulge in pleasure.

25:28.200 --> 25:29.030
But Prince Qi

25:29.720 --> 25:31.780
will never forget the fall of Qizhou.

25:32.530 --> 25:33.770
But I am not a pawn!

25:35.680 --> 25:37.720
My life and honor

25:38.200 --> 25:38.960
must never depend on

25:38.960 --> 25:40.510
your passing whims!

25:42.310 --> 25:43.750
Prince Jing'an's Household

25:43.750 --> 25:44.750
and the Beifu Army

25:45.400 --> 25:46.880
must both be contained!

25:47.550 --> 25:49.750
Are you counting on the noble families?

25:50.790 --> 25:52.240
You know better than I do

25:52.880 --> 25:54.810
that they are the true blight of Ye.

25:57.310 --> 25:58.000
Yizhi,

25:59.480 --> 26:01.400
if you rule your people
through manipulation,

26:01.400 --> 26:03.400
they will manipulate you in return.

26:03.920 --> 26:04.530
Why not

26:05.960 --> 26:06.920
try another way?

26:12.310 --> 26:15.160
Bravo! Bravo!

26:15.920 --> 26:17.400
Bravo!

26:21.200 --> 26:22.260
Where is the money?

26:22.830 --> 26:23.350
Where is my money?

26:23.350 --> 26:24.480
Listen, brat.

26:24.540 --> 26:26.270
You are not leaving today without paying.

26:26.270 --> 26:26.960
Give us the money!

26:26.960 --> 26:27.930
Give us the money!

26:27.930 --> 26:30.060
-Give us the money!
-Behave yourself!

26:31.600 --> 26:34.000
You should've done that earlier. Let's go.

26:43.520 --> 26:45.070
Mao, I am hungry.

26:54.600 --> 26:55.560
Thank you.

27:01.920 --> 27:02.590
Move!

27:02.750 --> 27:03.640
Out of the way!

27:07.790 --> 27:08.640
Xiao Wuyi,

27:08.790 --> 27:11.270
so many refugees are begging
outside Jiankang.

27:11.270 --> 27:13.270
Why is the Beifu Army doing nothing?

27:14.190 --> 27:15.240
Have you ever thought about

27:15.240 --> 27:17.240
what Ye will be like in the future?

27:18.310 --> 27:21.270
I hope for a Ye of peace and prosperity,

27:21.790 --> 27:24.440
with capable generals
defending the borders,

27:24.790 --> 27:26.920
a righteous and well-governed court,

27:27.030 --> 27:31.430
and scholars of both noble and humble origins
making full use of their talents.

27:46.070 --> 27:49.270
They are the scholars of humble origins
hiding in Xiyuan.

27:50.030 --> 27:51.030
Why were Liu Zhaolin and those

27:51.030 --> 27:52.760
poor scholars hiding in Xiyuan

27:53.560 --> 27:55.160
willing to help Xie Huaigui?

27:55.440 --> 27:56.570
It's simply because

27:56.830 --> 27:59.440
relying on the powerful is their only path
to an official career.

27:59.440 --> 28:01.850
If not forced by circumstances,

28:02.360 --> 28:05.690
what scholar would willingly
soil their brush and clothes?

28:11.410 --> 28:12.000
Tell me.

28:13.590 --> 28:15.520
Should I give them another chance?

28:16.000 --> 28:17.600
Your Highness saved my life.

28:18.120 --> 28:19.160
To me,

28:19.640 --> 28:20.440
Your Highness

28:20.720 --> 28:23.380
is a god who guided my soul
through the darkness.

28:23.590 --> 28:24.350
If today,

28:24.570 --> 28:26.720
Your Highness is willing
to give them another chance,

28:26.720 --> 28:28.210
they will surely
dedicate their entire lives

28:28.210 --> 28:29.380
to you.

28:33.750 --> 28:36.030
Forgive me, Your Highness. I misspoke.

28:45.380 --> 28:46.840
Get them some new clothes.

28:47.250 --> 28:47.860
Yes.

28:53.750 --> 28:55.350
We can establish the Nine-Rank System,

28:55.350 --> 28:59.440
with family background,
literary talent, and moral conduct

28:59.830 --> 29:01.310
as the criteria for ranking.

29:01.310 --> 29:03.550
Only nobles
can attain the upper ranks.

29:03.600 --> 29:07.330
You still see the Lantai gathering
as a private tool for the nobles.

29:07.920 --> 29:09.120
I have been Regent for 3 years.

29:09.120 --> 29:10.680
I established provincial schools

29:10.680 --> 29:12.080
and expanded libraries.

29:12.370 --> 29:15.110
Talents from humble origins
are no longer what they once were.

29:15.110 --> 29:15.770
Therefore,

29:16.590 --> 29:19.530
I will change the Lantai gathering
into spring examinations,

29:19.530 --> 29:22.830
letting the commoners and nobles
compete on equal footing.

29:22.830 --> 29:26.590
Your Highness, the hierarchy of rites
is like a guiding star.

29:26.720 --> 29:28.880
If old systems are recklessly changed,

29:28.880 --> 29:31.610
I fear the order of the realm
will fall into chaos.

29:33.070 --> 29:35.730
Master, you have helped me
reach this position.

29:36.270 --> 29:39.600
What's the point of talking about
the order of the realm now?

29:42.070 --> 29:45.640
Your Highness, holding a spring exam
requires massive effort.

29:46.270 --> 29:48.400
Moreover, the children of noble families

29:48.400 --> 29:50.270
have studied the classics since childhood.

29:50.270 --> 29:52.440
The great scholars are all at our schools.

29:52.440 --> 29:53.440
And the academies

29:54.000 --> 29:56.530
are all operated
by the major noble families.

29:57.030 --> 29:59.640
They spend fortunes to gather the wise

30:00.030 --> 30:03.030
and have already recruited
all the elite of the realm.

30:04.030 --> 30:04.880
Could it be

30:05.070 --> 30:08.530
that you are afraid the nobles
can't beat the humble scholars?

30:10.070 --> 30:12.830
If Your Highness insists on doing this,

30:13.750 --> 30:15.550
I have one condition.

30:16.270 --> 30:19.880
Pose a challenging question
for all students and have them discuss

30:19.880 --> 30:23.210
the difficulties and solutions
in waterway construction.

30:23.570 --> 30:25.480
This is a universal challenge.

30:26.190 --> 30:29.400
Let's see which of the two groups,
the nobles and the humble scholars,

30:29.400 --> 30:31.600
truly understands Ye's state affairs.

30:32.960 --> 30:34.560
If, as Your Highness claims,

30:35.270 --> 30:37.670
the nobles can't beat the humble scholars,

30:37.960 --> 30:39.720
I am willing to retire,

30:40.020 --> 30:41.080
reopen my academy,

30:41.310 --> 30:42.350
devote myself to scholarship,

30:42.350 --> 30:45.080
and no longer
get involved in political affairs.

30:46.400 --> 30:47.460
You must be joking.

30:47.680 --> 30:49.310
I approve of this.

30:53.550 --> 30:54.790
[Imperial Academy]

30:55.790 --> 30:57.070
The time for this year's Lantai gathering
has been set.

30:57.070 --> 30:58.310
What? When?

30:58.310 --> 30:59.030
When? Let me see.

30:59.030 --> 30:59.790
Wait.

31:02.710 --> 31:03.960
By order of the Eastern Palace,

31:03.960 --> 31:06.290
this year's Lantai gathering is canceled

31:06.510 --> 31:07.750
and replaced by a spring examination.

31:07.750 --> 31:09.000
Talents will be selected

31:09.000 --> 31:10.930
regardless of family background.

31:11.000 --> 31:11.920
Regardless of family background?

31:11.920 --> 31:15.000
-Canceled? A spring examination?
-Regardless of family background?

31:15.000 --> 31:16.640
It's an order from the Eastern Palace?

31:16.640 --> 31:17.440
Xie Huaigui!

31:17.590 --> 31:19.790
Xie Huaigui, come out!

31:19.790 --> 31:21.400
Why is the Lantai gathering canceled?

31:21.400 --> 31:23.640
Why is it canceled?
Why set a spring examination?

31:23.640 --> 31:25.400
-Xie Huaigui!
-Xie Huaigui!

31:25.750 --> 31:26.750
Come out!

31:27.580 --> 31:28.200
Return to the mansion.

31:28.200 --> 31:29.000
Why is it canceled?

31:29.000 --> 31:30.000
Xie Huaigui!

31:30.650 --> 31:32.650
The spring exam will start in 3 days.

31:32.800 --> 31:35.180
Your brother spends all day
reading storybooks.

31:35.180 --> 31:36.740
His heart lies not here,

31:36.850 --> 31:38.720
but among the mountains and rivers.

31:38.720 --> 31:40.550
He frequents music houses all day.

31:40.550 --> 31:41.750
The gazette says

31:42.000 --> 31:43.070
this examination

31:43.070 --> 31:45.720
only has 2 subjects:
Confucian classics and policy essays.

31:45.720 --> 31:47.550
Students take the exam anonymously,

31:47.550 --> 31:48.750
and papers are graded anonymously.

31:48.750 --> 31:50.240
Five matches are ranked as superior,

31:50.240 --> 31:51.750
three or four as middle,

31:51.880 --> 31:53.010
and two as inferior.

31:53.750 --> 31:55.480
I don't know if it's true or not.

31:55.480 --> 31:56.400
Yuanji.

31:57.000 --> 31:58.110
You are now

31:58.110 --> 31:59.920
the head of our He family.

32:00.100 --> 32:01.480
If your father and brother

32:01.480 --> 32:02.960
fail to secure a good future,

32:02.960 --> 32:05.370
who in the entire He family

32:05.400 --> 32:06.800
will truly submit to you?

32:07.160 --> 32:09.830
Yuanji! Did you hear me?

32:09.830 --> 32:12.230
You need to talk to your father
and brother.

32:13.080 --> 32:14.420
Throughout history, talent selection

32:14.420 --> 32:16.790
has always been based on
family background.

32:16.790 --> 32:18.380
As the saying goes, those of humble origins
cannot reach high ranks,

32:18.380 --> 32:19.680
and those from noble families
do not fall to low ranks.

32:19.680 --> 32:21.250
Prince Qi has now
set a spring examination.

32:21.250 --> 32:22.320
Regardless of noble or humble status,

32:22.320 --> 32:23.190
or connections,

32:23.190 --> 32:24.480
as long as one has real talent,

32:24.480 --> 32:25.740
they can take the exam.

32:26.310 --> 32:28.310
If they truly appoint officials
based on ability,

32:28.310 --> 32:29.440
it would be a great achievement.

32:29.440 --> 32:30.920
But they are unwilling to take the exam.

32:30.920 --> 32:32.310
What's the point?

32:34.290 --> 32:35.090
Auntie He.

32:39.940 --> 32:40.820
Don't worry.

32:41.120 --> 32:42.780
I have come up with a good idea.

32:43.110 --> 32:45.510
Isn't the path forward for the He family

32:45.650 --> 32:46.850
right in front of you?

32:47.350 --> 32:48.240
Your Highness,

32:48.450 --> 32:50.300
are you making fun of us?

32:52.050 --> 32:52.770
Yuanji,

32:53.120 --> 32:54.190
think about it.

32:54.430 --> 32:56.030
I'm serious about this.

32:56.050 --> 32:58.450
Yuanji, don't listen to her nonsense.

32:58.640 --> 33:00.100
It could cost us our lives.

33:01.270 --> 33:02.130
Your Highness,

33:02.590 --> 33:03.590
please go back.

33:04.550 --> 33:05.030
Please go back.

33:05.030 --> 33:05.680
Yuanji,

33:05.680 --> 33:06.750
I am serious.

33:06.750 --> 33:07.640
Think about it.

33:49.980 --> 33:51.750
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

33:55.750 --> 33:57.320
You are making me dizzy.

33:58.270 --> 34:00.870
I wonder what rank Yuanji received
in the exam.

34:01.440 --> 34:02.570
The results are out!

34:05.200 --> 34:05.880
The results are out?

34:05.880 --> 34:06.510
Yes.

34:06.680 --> 34:07.200
What rank?

34:07.200 --> 34:07.860
First rank.

34:08.040 --> 34:08.590
Really?

34:09.710 --> 34:10.510
Now Yuanji

34:10.510 --> 34:12.110
can finally hold her head high.

34:12.110 --> 34:13.110
She is a female Academician now

34:13.110 --> 34:14.969
and will become a court official.

34:14.969 --> 34:16.170
I need to design

34:16.199 --> 34:18.000
a ceremonial hairpiece for her.

34:18.030 --> 34:18.960
Where is she now?

34:19.840 --> 34:20.760
She has entered the Eastern Palace

34:20.760 --> 34:22.760
and is about to be granted the title.

34:26.030 --> 34:28.110
He Yuan,
the second child of the fifth branch

34:28.110 --> 34:29.920
of the He family in Yingchuan,

34:29.940 --> 34:32.360
topped the list
in this imperial examination.

34:32.360 --> 34:33.590
He can enter the Imperial Academy

34:33.590 --> 34:34.960
with the title of Academician,

34:34.960 --> 34:37.080
ranked Upper First Grade.

34:37.480 --> 34:39.530
He Yuan, the second child of the fifth branch
of the He family in Yingchuan,

34:39.530 --> 34:40.590
pays her respects.

34:44.679 --> 34:45.360
Rise.

34:48.110 --> 34:49.570
Thank you, Your Highness.

34:59.000 --> 34:59.800
Wait.

35:13.650 --> 35:15.050
May I ask, Your Highness,

35:15.710 --> 35:17.640
why you specifically chose He Yuan

35:17.710 --> 35:19.880
as the top Academician
in the spring examination?

35:19.880 --> 35:21.030
Is it because of the question about

35:21.030 --> 35:24.360
the difficulties and solutions
in waterway construction?

35:24.440 --> 35:25.970
You're right, Grand Tutor.

35:26.240 --> 35:27.230
For this question,

35:27.230 --> 35:28.800
all examinees quoted the late Emperor's

35:28.800 --> 35:31.200
"Wenxi Treatise" on waterway management,

35:31.550 --> 35:34.280
using wooden stakes and wicker
to reinforce the riverbanks.

35:34.280 --> 35:36.670
But He Yuan proposed

35:36.920 --> 35:39.120
the method of bamboo cage with pebbles.

35:39.180 --> 35:40.980
He Yuan, explain it to everyone.

35:44.590 --> 35:46.030
The method of bamboo cage with pebbles

35:46.030 --> 35:47.320
means weaving bamboo into cages,

35:47.320 --> 35:50.030
filling them with pebbles,
and sinking them into the river.

35:50.030 --> 35:52.320
The toughness of bamboo cages
and the weight of the pebbles

35:52.320 --> 35:53.740
can both stabilize the riverbank

35:53.740 --> 35:55.880
and withstand the impact
of the water flow.

35:55.880 --> 35:57.630
This is a method of overcoming
hardness with softness.

35:57.630 --> 35:59.710
Let me ask you.
How did you, a child of a noble family,

35:59.710 --> 36:01.170
come to know the solution?

36:01.200 --> 36:02.110
Your Highness,

36:02.630 --> 36:04.880
I learned this from a criminal.

36:05.310 --> 36:06.100
A criminal?

36:06.840 --> 36:07.320
A criminal?

36:07.320 --> 36:09.320
I brought him here today.

36:09.730 --> 36:10.560
His name is...

36:11.440 --> 36:13.070
Liu Zhaolin.

36:30.320 --> 36:31.920
I'm Liu Zhaolin, a criminal.

36:32.110 --> 36:33.370
Greetings, Prince Qi.

36:34.000 --> 36:35.150
Liu Zhaolin?

36:36.820 --> 36:38.050
Aren't you dead?

36:38.930 --> 36:40.160
Grand Tutor wanted me

36:40.190 --> 36:41.240
to die in the Court of Judicial Review,

36:41.240 --> 36:42.840
but Young Lord Xiao saved me.

36:43.730 --> 36:45.660
I met Grand Tutor in the bookstore.

36:46.360 --> 36:47.840
He said that if I wanted to stand out,

36:47.840 --> 36:49.640
I must first learn to bow my head.

36:49.840 --> 36:50.880
As long as I forged the account books

36:50.880 --> 36:52.420
of Prince Jing'an's Mansion for him,

36:52.420 --> 36:54.710
framing their family
for colluding with foreign enemies,

36:54.710 --> 36:57.570
he would give me a chance
to enter official service.

36:57.720 --> 36:58.840
So I bowed my head.

36:59.400 --> 37:00.670
I deceived the former Heir's Consort

37:00.670 --> 37:02.270
of Prince Jing'an's Mansion

37:02.430 --> 37:05.280
and tricked her into giving me
the Xiaos' private letters.

37:05.280 --> 37:07.260
In Lane 3 of Shanghe Ward, a place
arranged by the Grand Tutor,

37:07.260 --> 37:09.120
I spent 3 whole months practicing

37:09.710 --> 37:10.670
until my forged handwriting

37:10.670 --> 37:12.350
was convincing enough to pass as genuine.

37:12.350 --> 37:15.660
But later, when the case
of Prince Jing'an's Mansion broke out,

37:15.660 --> 37:16.990
he wanted to silence me.

37:18.540 --> 37:19.730
I saw the method
of bamboo cage with pebbles

37:19.730 --> 37:21.560
in the Grand Tutor's study.

37:22.420 --> 37:25.340
He has been studying
this method for over a decade.

37:28.880 --> 37:30.550
Yes, I was the one who ordered

37:31.000 --> 37:31.920
Liu Zhaolin and others to fabricate

37:31.920 --> 37:34.550
the charges
against Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

37:34.550 --> 37:36.280
And I have indeed been studying

37:36.280 --> 37:37.920
the method of bamboo cage with pebbles.

37:37.920 --> 37:39.070
But do you know

37:39.070 --> 37:41.070
the origin of this method?

37:42.130 --> 37:43.520
Back then, the An and Lu families

37:43.520 --> 37:46.890
used exactly this method
for waterway management.

37:47.610 --> 37:50.320
But at that time,
this method was framed as evidence

37:50.320 --> 37:52.150
that the An and Lu families
had deliberately damaged the waterways

37:52.150 --> 37:53.480
and colluded with Northern Qin.

37:53.480 --> 37:54.630
They were charged with treason.

37:54.630 --> 37:56.000
As a result, for over 20 years,

37:56.000 --> 37:57.600
no one dared use this method.

37:58.030 --> 38:00.490
If Your Highness acknowledges this method,

38:00.880 --> 38:03.480
that would prove that Emperor Wenxi
was mistaken

38:03.480 --> 38:06.740
and that the An and Lu families
were wrongfully convicted!

38:12.440 --> 38:13.000
Brother.

38:18.400 --> 38:20.730
The model of the bamboo cage with pebbles?

38:21.440 --> 38:22.230
Xiao Wuyi,

38:22.260 --> 38:25.790
you knew all along that Brother and I
were studying this method?

38:26.570 --> 38:27.770
Everything is ready.

38:32.300 --> 38:33.010
Xiao Wuyi,

38:33.550 --> 38:36.750
are you going to clear
the An and Lu families' names today?

38:37.410 --> 38:38.180
If so,

38:38.320 --> 38:39.920
I'm afraid the posthumous reputations
of Emperor and Empress Wenxi

38:39.920 --> 38:41.120
cannot be preserved.

38:42.070 --> 38:43.070
I don't care about

38:43.320 --> 38:44.180
the Grand Tutor

38:44.510 --> 38:45.190
or the past.

38:45.510 --> 38:48.230
What I care about
is how to construct the waterways,

38:48.230 --> 38:49.630
how to save the people

38:49.840 --> 38:51.400
from the suffering of floods,

38:51.400 --> 38:53.380
and how to open the grain canal
to the Northern Border as soon as possible.

38:53.380 --> 38:54.710
If this method is right,

38:54.880 --> 38:56.210
it shouldn't be buried.

38:57.030 --> 38:57.840
Xie Jiayu,

38:59.000 --> 39:00.460
are you willing to help me?

39:03.470 --> 39:06.360
The case of the An and Lu families' treason
has long been settled.

39:06.360 --> 39:08.690
And this method
of bamboo cages with pebbles

39:08.690 --> 39:10.620
has not been used for over 20 years.

39:11.000 --> 39:12.320
Then how can we prove

39:12.590 --> 39:14.630
whether this method works or not?

39:17.510 --> 39:19.240
Then please allow me the chance

39:19.670 --> 39:21.880
to prove it today in the Eastern Palace.

39:24.320 --> 39:26.850
I, Xiao Yao,
pay my respects to Your Highness.

39:46.550 --> 39:47.960
I, Xiao Yao, a disgraced subject,

39:47.960 --> 39:49.820
pay my respects to Your Highness.

39:51.500 --> 39:52.890
Ever since the waterway collapsed,

39:52.890 --> 39:54.620
I have not slept a single night.

39:55.120 --> 39:56.750
Fortunately,
I received guidance from Mr. Liu,

39:56.750 --> 39:58.510
and with the help of the Heir's Consort,

39:58.510 --> 40:00.250
I crafted this bamboo cage with pebbles.

40:00.250 --> 40:03.230
I humbly ask Your Highness
to grant permission for a trial.

40:03.230 --> 40:04.360
Permission granted.

40:04.360 --> 40:05.820
Thank you, Your Highness.

40:09.580 --> 40:10.310
Assemble it.

40:12.370 --> 40:12.970
Add water.

40:48.390 --> 40:49.720
The pebbles in this cage

40:49.960 --> 40:52.760
must be 70% angular stones
and 30% rounded stones,

40:52.840 --> 40:55.360
with the stones arranged
from the bottom up in a spiral shape.

40:55.360 --> 40:56.690
The 3rd piece is the key.

40:57.230 --> 40:58.760
If a fully round one is used,

40:58.960 --> 41:01.490
the water will disperse
like a defeated army.

41:11.400 --> 41:12.030
It's done.

41:12.830 --> 41:14.480
Look, the water flow has slowed down.

41:14.480 --> 41:16.010
The house didn't collapse.

41:20.150 --> 41:22.080
I wonder if what you have seen today

41:22.330 --> 41:24.860
can untie the knot in your heart,
Grand Tutor.

41:35.760 --> 41:36.620
Your Highness.

41:37.360 --> 41:39.810
If we don't correct
Emperor Wenxi's mistake today,

41:39.810 --> 41:41.360
I'm sure more people

41:41.360 --> 41:42.960
will suffer from the floods.

41:43.230 --> 41:46.860
Your Highness, please give your judgment.

41:54.800 --> 41:57.540
Back then,
to seize power from the noble families,

41:57.540 --> 41:58.550
Emperor Wenxi used
the waterway construction case as a pretext

41:58.550 --> 42:01.030
to frame the An and Lu families
for colluding with Northern Qin.

42:01.030 --> 42:03.490
It plunged Ye
into endless internal strife,

42:03.680 --> 42:06.550
allowing Northern Qin to take the opportunity
to march south and overrun the Capital.

42:06.550 --> 42:09.880
This tragedy was single-handedly
caused by Emperor Wenxi,

42:10.030 --> 42:12.070
and it was a disaster born from the conflict between
the noble families and the common people.

42:12.070 --> 42:14.150
If we do not abandon the divide
between nobles and commoners

42:14.150 --> 42:16.280
and clear the names
of the An and Lu families,

42:16.280 --> 42:19.280
the tragedy of the Capital
will surely repeat itself.

42:20.840 --> 42:23.100
Emperor and Empress Wenxi were not gods,

42:23.340 --> 42:24.230
and the world should not be defined

42:24.230 --> 42:26.000
only by the divide
between nobles and commoners.

42:26.000 --> 42:29.000
Above all, the world cannot depend
on a single person.

42:29.230 --> 42:30.590
And that person in your hearts,

42:30.590 --> 42:32.450
the god-like Crown Prince Wenxi,

42:33.360 --> 42:34.150
actually

42:35.560 --> 42:38.000
died long ago on his way south
to Jiankang.

42:57.480 --> 42:58.480
Pass on my decree.

42:59.050 --> 43:01.310
Clear the names of the An and Lu families.

43:01.890 --> 43:03.280
All false charges against them

43:03.280 --> 43:04.410
shall be dismissed.

43:04.880 --> 43:06.140
Take in their orphans,

43:06.320 --> 43:07.800
allow them
to return to their native places,

43:07.800 --> 43:09.710
and send them to the Imperial Academy
for education.

43:09.710 --> 43:10.400
Also,

43:10.840 --> 43:12.960
Xiao Yao shall be stripped
of all official titles

43:12.960 --> 43:16.890
and banished to Lingnan to address
the flooding along the grain canal.

43:18.150 --> 43:19.920
I will do my utmost

43:20.190 --> 43:21.230
for Ye

43:21.510 --> 43:22.630
until my dying day.

43:33.210 --> 43:35.960
My wish is fulfilled.

43:37.460 --> 43:38.270
I...

43:39.870 --> 43:41.400
am willing to plead guilty.

43:44.860 --> 43:47.190
Then there will be no further punishment.

43:47.630 --> 43:49.950
I hope you will retire
and return to your hometown,

43:49.950 --> 43:51.150
reopen your academy,

43:51.360 --> 43:52.970
devote yourself to scholarship,

43:52.970 --> 43:55.700
and no longer
get involved in political affairs.

43:58.280 --> 44:00.760
I accept the decree.

44:04.240 --> 44:06.630
Liu Zhaolin and the scholars
from Lane 3 of Shanghe Ward

44:06.630 --> 44:08.200
forged handwriting and account books

44:08.200 --> 44:10.200
to frame Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

44:10.630 --> 44:13.190
Considering that this arose from
the divide between nobles and commoners,

44:13.190 --> 44:14.480
and that they have acknowledged
their wrongdoing,

44:14.480 --> 44:15.680
I shall show leniency

44:16.000 --> 44:17.530
and banish them 800 li away.

44:17.740 --> 44:18.870
I accept the decree.

44:23.770 --> 44:26.150
Your Highness, the divide between
nobles and commoners

44:26.150 --> 44:27.280
has long plagued Ye.

44:27.530 --> 44:29.260
Please eradicate it at its root

44:30.000 --> 44:32.190
and establish the spring examination
as a permanent system

44:32.190 --> 44:33.320
to ensure fairness.

44:37.230 --> 44:37.880
Granted.
